<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="24Sep1921"><font color="red">24 September 1921</font>, <cite>Letters III</cite> (JJ to Valery Larbaud): I am nearly dead with work and eyes. Sent <cite>Penelope</cite> to the printers so that you may have it to read when you  come here. All will be ready for you on the 2 October. The <cite>Ithaca</cite> episode I shall put in order in October &hellip; You will scarcely recognise parts of <cite>Ulysses</cite> I have worked so much on them</div>
